                </p>
                <p>
                    Aṉu<hi rend="grantha">pa</hi>vikku
                    <lb n="26" break="no"/>mm iṭat=tu y-inta maṉai muppatt=u ṉālukkuḷ Uṇṭāṉa
                    <lb n="27"/>ni<hi rend="grantha">dhi</hi>-ni<hi rend="grantha">kṣepa-jala-pāṣā</hi>ṇa-<hi rend="grantha">Akṣi</hi>ṇ<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice>-<hi rend="grantha">Ākā</hi>
