                    <lb n="30"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṟayaṅkaḷukkum yō<hi rend="grantha">gy</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">M</hi>m-āka puṉa <gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">ma</hi>
                    <lb n="31"/>ṇa nira<hi rend="grantha">pekṣam-āka</hi> paṟṟi Aṉupavittuk <supplied reason="lost">ko</supplied>
                    <lb n="32" break="no"/>ḷḷa-k kaṭ<choice><sic>ai</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>var ākavum
                </p>   
                <p>
                    A<unclear>ṉu</unclear>pavikkum iṭattu I
                    <lb n="33" break="no"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kku kala nillai kala nuḷavākat tōṟṟiṟa paṭil
                    <lb n="34"/>nāṅkaḷē muṉṉiṉṟu kalaṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <unclear cert="low">t=</unclear>tu kuṭukka kaṭa<seg rend="check">vē mā<!--EF: ri--></seg>
